snippet.title: Modern War Institute
snippet.description: Established by the United States Military Academy’s (USMA) Superintendent as a Center of Excellence in 2015, the Modern War Institute (MWI) promotes informed debate and discussion among military & national security professionals, policymakers, and academics to advance the Study of War--  the ethical design, generation, support, and application of land power (and associated Joint, Combined, and Inter-Agency capabilities) for today as well as 10-15 years into the future.
